reviewText: Makes the "Wild, Wild, Wild West" look kinda Sissy-fied.  Comes complete with those rare moments you would want to repeat at work except that you are smart enough to realize: 1) They probably wouldn't get the reference & 2) You'ld be dragged into Human Resources so fast your head would spin around and you'ld puke green-pea-soup all over your supervisor.
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: This dramatic western has not only every single episode to enjoy but as well it comes with background information; historic information and it's an awesome never to be seen again set of the most exciting time in history.  It's awesome!!!
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: A great series once you get used to the language of that era. The bonus by the writer is just essential to watch before you start watching the series to understand just how real this all has been ....I loved it.
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: I purchases these DVD sets because I loved the series and wanted to be able to watch them whenever I wanted.  Still waiting for the "finale" movies.
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: "Deadwood" is a series we watch entirely every year. Great Cast; well-researched and well-written story line. We only regret that they did not continue with a Season four and beyond!
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: Deadwood is based on the wild west and some of the characters and events are based on factual history. The language and the actions of this camp were acceptable for that time and certain members. I love watching this show, its realistic of the era. I dont understand why someone would waste their time to write a negative review of something they obviously have not watched, but to each their own. I dont live my life like this obviously, but it doesnt mean I dont enjoy the show.
summary: Great portrayel of the wild wild west!!!
Title: Deadwood - The Complete First Two Seasons

reviewText: I bought these for my husband and he and his crew absolutely love them!  They watch these on the road.
